a71fda","tid":1329963,"uid":49774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"肯聽大眾意見 唔會一意孤行 係各有各做情況下真係好重要<br />\n我知好多泛民都會犯張超雄既錯 但唔該都學下野<br />\n懸崖勒馬真係好重要"},{"pid":"39ed0b868777170b97224deaa75ba5b7af0c94bc","tid":1329963,"uid":20696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔覺佢有咁高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但出黎嘅效果都起碼話俾人知<br />\n真正聽民意要點<br />\n撤回可以好簡單<br />\n<br />\n<code>1）有人講咗「唔好再覆」就唔好爭住屌一毛、恥笑一毛，亦唔好跟住留「唔好再覆」，否則等同推po。2）俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。3）新聞po睇日期先覆，小心一毛伎倆：有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po。最後，721去遊行！</code>"},{"pid":"898420701d1e1d7294bd471b07bdc50698addb23","tid":1329963,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d331b3574c7e70749bfdf0c7e6326d30302647c7","tid":1329963,"uid":263555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4b75b4c7b7a4f477213d04e86235c16b8159a3a","tid":1329963,"uid":49774,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9fd589b5f9845cdb8be072881b04bd2daaa18ea8","tid":1329963,"uid":263555,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"條友就低能既<br />\n擺明係負碌達至上述效果<br />\n<br />\n點知屌你政府仲低能<br />\n走去accept"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"我就覺得佢係懶醒 搶風頭 加左膠上腦先會草擬份野出黎<br />\n但都無可否認埋尾果下撤回真係致命一擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332f9c06a3cc610278a1d18de8a3df3c66843440","tid":1329963,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ed0b868777170b97224deaa75ba5b7af0c94bc","tid":1329963,"uid":20696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔覺佢有咁高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但出黎嘅效果都起碼話俾人知<br />\n真正聽民意要點<br />\n撤回可以好簡單<br />\